{"title":"100% Altis Gravel Helmet is 100% for gravel riders, w/ Smartshock rotational protection","link":"https://bikerumor.com/2021/09/14/100-altis-gravel-helmet-is-100-for-gravel-riders-w-smartshock-rotational-protection/","date":1631640227000,"content":"<div id=\"readability-page-1\" class=\"page\"><div><img width=\"800\" height=\"534\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/14131500/100-altis-gravel-white-helmet-800x534.jpg?ezimgfmt=rs%3Adevice%2Frscb28-1\" alt=\"100% altis gravel helmet good coverage\" loading=\"eager\" srcset=\"\" sizes=\"\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb28 src ng ngcb28 srcset\"><header></header><p>Support us! BikeRumor may earn a small commission from affiliate links in this article. <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/privacy\" target=\"_blank\">Learn more</a>.</p></div><div role=\"main\"><article id=\"post-271498\" role=\"article\" itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"http://schema.org/BlogPosting\"><section itemprop=\"text\"><p>100% have released a gravel-specific version of the Altis Trail helmet. The lack of peak is what sets the Altis Gravel apart from its mountain bike counterpart, shaving weight and improving air channeling through the front-facing vents.&nbsp;</p><h2>100% Altis Gravel Helmet</h2><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/14131451/100-altis-gravel-helmet-men.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/14131451/100-altis-gravel-helmet-men.jpg\" alt=\"100% altis gravel helmet mens black\" width=\"1600\" height=\"1067\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/14131451/100-altis-gravel-helmet-men.jpg 1600w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/14131451/100-altis-gravel-helmet-men-297x198.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.